  "body": "## Status against clients\r\n  > Lighthouse \r\n   - [x] Manual interfacing \r\n     - [x] Local testnet setup with client beacons and validators forming fully functional chain\r\n     - [x] Interfacing/connection with the beacon node\r\n     - [x] API Interoperability\r\n       - [x] request  and process api responses from beacon chain\r\n\r\n   - [x] Functionality\r\n     - [x] Publish Attestations\r\n     - [x] Publish Block\r\n     - [x] Get the finality going ( 2/3 of validator set only with lodestar)\r\n     - [x] Recover the finality ( join 1/2 of validator set after multi epoch finality delay and nodes achieve finality)\r\n   - [ ] Interop tests integrated\r\n     - [ ] Docker Setup for the local testnet of client beacons\r\n     - [ ] API endpoints in spec\r\n     - [ ] Functionality Tests\r\n\r\n### Progress /Outstanding Issues\r\n> Subtasks/issues\r\n - [x]  casingMap to match the case\r\n - [x] A way to Deal with fields yet not operation and hence mightnot be in the beacon response for config (like merge fields:  `TERMINAL_TOTAL_DIFFICULTY`, `MERGE_FORK_VERSION` ...), are not available in stable branch  of lighthouse, and can't be assumed to be available untill the respective fork date #3369\r\n - [x] `produceBlock` api call from validator to lighhouse beacon is not working #3370\r\n ",
